**SCP-6468 - pvp potion by dado**
//This article is an entry into the [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/department-contest|2022 Department Contest]]].//

[[/=]]
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]
[[table style="width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(var(--medium-accent)); border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--medium-accent));"]]
[[row]]
[[cell]]
